amp; Trend Tracking<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1540\">Beyond replying, we observe how your community <em data-start=\"1530\" data-end=\"1537\">feels<\/em>.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1848\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1667\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1667\">We monitor the tone of comments and messages, identifying patterns in praise, frustration, or frequently asked questions.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1668\" data-end=\"1848\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1670\" data-end=\"1848\">Emerging topics, viral mentions, or negative sentiment are flagged and reported in real time.<br data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1766\" \/>This proactive tracking helps you make informed decisions and address risks early.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1850\" data-end=\"1889\">Comment Moderation &amp; Spam Control<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1890\" data-end=\"1927\">A clean page is a trustworthy page.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1928\" data-end=\"2187\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1928\" data-end=\"2011\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"2011\">We hide or remove spam, offensive language, bot comments, and irrelevant links.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2187\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2014\" data-end=\"2187\">At the same time, we highlight and engage with user-generated content (UGC), customer shoutouts, and brand mentions \u2014 helping amplify positive sentiment and community pride.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2189\" data-end=\"2215\">Reporting &amp; Insights<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2252\">We don\u2019t just manage \u2014 we measure.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2253\" data-end=\"2528\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2253\" data-end=\"2374\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2255\" data-end=\"2374\">Weekly and monthly reports include summaries of engagement, response rates, sentiment trends