operate in isolation, but as part of a broader digital strategy.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"\" data-start=\"245\" data-end=\"323\">Sample Community Engagement Metrics<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"325\" data-end=\"645\">Case Study: for Oxford University Press East Africa<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"325\" data-end=\"645\">At Aminifu Digital, we measure success through actionable metrics, not just vanity numbers. Our community management support for Oxford University Press East Africa (OUPEA) demonstrates how structured, daily engagement transforms audience responsiveness, brand sentiment, and operational efficiency across digital platforms.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"720\">Here\u2019s a snapshot of key community metrics we improved in under 6 months:<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"722\" data-end=\"745\">Response Time<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"1005\"><strong data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"757\">Before:<\/strong> 12\u201324 hours average response<br data-start=\"786\" data-end=\"789\" \/><strong data-start=\"789\" data-end=\"799\">After:<\/strong> Under 3 hours on weekdays, under 6 hours on weekends<br data-start=\"852\" data-end=\"855\" \/>We reduced the average inbox and comment response time by <strong data-start=\"913\" data-end=\"920\">75%<\/strong>, ensuring faster resolution of customer queries, book orders, and partner enquiries.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1033\">Engagement Rate<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1285\"><strong data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1045\">Before:<\/strong> 0.9%<br data-start=\"1050\" data-end=\"1053\" \/><strong data-start=\"1053\" data-end=\"1063\">After:<\/strong> 5%-16.5% average on Facebook<br data-start=\"1106\" data-end=\"1109\" \/>With active comment moderation, timely replies, and strategic content tagging, we exponentially increased the average engagement rate, keeping OUPEA\u2019s content visible and conversation-driven.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1287\" data-end=\"1313\">Sentiment Score<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1314\" data-end=\"1626\"><strong data-start=\"1314\" data-end=\"1325\">Before:<\/strong> Mixed\/neutral<br data-start=\"1371\" data-end=\"1374\" \/><strong data-start=\"1374\" data-end=\"1384\">After:<\/strong> 80%+ positive sentiment consistently across posts and campaigns<br data-start=\"1448\" data-end=\"1451\" \/>Our sentiment tracking tools helped us spot trends early and steer conversations positively \u2014 especially during sensitive periods like textbook release cycles or exam seasons.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1628\" data-end=\"1668\">Average Query Resolution Time<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1669\" data-end=\"1928\"><strong data-start=\"1669\" data-end=\"1680\">Before:<\/strong> 2\u20133 days<br data-start=\"1689\" data-end=\"1692\" \/><strong data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1702\">After:<\/strong> Resolved or escalated within 24 hours<br data-start=\"1740\" data-end=\"1743\" \/>Thanks to pre-approved FAQs and live coordination with internal teams, most queries (including order-related and publishing requests) were closed or handed over <strong data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1927\">within the same day<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"1962\">Daily Active Audience<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1963\" data-end=\"2261\"><strong data-start=\"1963\" data-end=\"1974\">Growth:<\/strong> 3,200+ new engaged users added in the first 3 months<br data-start=\"2027\" data-end=\"2030\" \/>We kept conversations active across Facebook, Instagram, and LinkedIn by replying to every relevant comment, reacting to audience posts, and acknowledging community contributions \u2014 from teachers and authors to students and parents.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2441\">These are not automated results \u2014 they\u2019re the product of deliberate, daily engagement. And they\u2019re replicable for any brand serious about social growth and reputation management. These results illustrate the power of professional Community Management Services when delivered consistently and in line with audience expectations.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717845133697{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; bg_color_value=&#8221;#f4f4f4&#8243; el_id=&#8221;!\/contact&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-1797695ec0cca1367\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-1797695ec0cca1367 uvc-6579  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"line_with_icon\" data-hline_width=\"100\" data-hicon_type=\"selector\" data-hborder_style=\"solid\" data-hborder_height=\"5\" data-hborder_color=\"#3697ca\" data-icon_width=\"32\" data-hfixer=\"5\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-1797695ec0cca1367 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"--font-weight:theme;\">Tired of Generic Posts and Poor Engagement?<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer line_with_icon\" style=\"topheight:32px;\"><div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper  \"><div class=\"align-icon\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<div class=\"aio-icon none \"  style=\"color:#3697ca;font-size:32px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"fas fa-angle-down\"><\/i>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-1797695ec0cca1367 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;margin-bottom:20px;\